resources.description: In this paper, some exact traveling wave solutions of (2+1) dimensional PKP equation and the fifth-order SK equation are established by a generalized sub-ODE method. The method appears to be efficient in seeking exact solutions of nonlinear equations.
resources.name: Traveling Wave Solutions for Some Nonlinear Differential Equations by a Generalized Sub-ODE Method ——Traveling Wave Solutions for Some Differential Equations

name: traveling-wave-solutions-for-some-nonlinear-differential-equations
